        <li>Min-width (px)</li>
        <li>Max-width (px)</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
    <li><strong>Extensible Styles:</strong> Cell templates use a styles array approach for easy extension with additional CSS properties</li>
    <li><strong>Modern CSS:</strong> Uses CSS width properties instead of deprecated HTML width attributes</li>
  </ul>

